suite.doc:
Example test cases using the keyword-driven testing approach.
All tests contain a workflow constructed from keywords in ``CalculatorLibrary.py``. Creating new tests or editing existing is easy even for people without programming skills.
The _keyword-driven_ appoach works well for normal test automation, but the _gherkin_ style might be even better if also business people need to understand tests. If the same workflow needs to repeated multiple times, it is best to use to the _data-driven_ approach.
